# ── Vercel: contact form (Resend) ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Add these in Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables (Production + Preview).
RESEND_API_KEY=
CONTACT_TO_EMAIL=info@zarmediagroup.com
# Must be a domain/sender verified in Resend (not onboarding@ for production volume).
RESEND_FROM=Zar Media Group <notifications@your-verified-domain.com>

# ── Optional: local or legacy hosting ───────────────────────────────────────
# While still on cPanel with PHP mail, you can point the form at PHP during build:
# VITE_CONTACT_ENDPOINT=/mail.php
